    <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
      <p><font size="2"><img src="luminare.jpg" width="135" height="250" align="left" alt="Luminare Pasinia">Firiona 
        Vieに居るLuminare Pasinia (loc -3960, 2630) からIksar変身Spell Questを受ける事が出来ます。</font></p>
      <p><font size="2"><b>You say, 'Hail, Luminare Pasinia'</b><br>
        Luminare Pasinia waves her hands as if to cast a spell. 'GREETINGS!! I 
        am the Luminare of Firiona. By decree of his royal highness, King Thex, 
        I am here to research spells and artifacts. I have much to do. I welcome 
        any enchanter who offers to [assist the great Luminare].'</font></p>
      <p><font size="2"><b>You say, 'i will assist the great luminare'</b><br>
        Luminare Pasinia says 'And great I am, indeed!! Alas, not great enough 
        to be everywhere at once. I would gladly reward you if you would [collect 
        components] for me.'</font></p>
      <p><font size="2"><b>You say, 'i will collect components'</b><br>
        Luminare Pasinia says 'Then go into the wilds beyond this outpost and 
        upon your return, you shall give to me the powder of Nok, heart of ice, 
        a Ton warrior totem and a sabertooth tiger mane. This shall earn you knowledge 
        of an enchanter spell I have recently scribed.' </font></p>
      <p><font size="2">４つのItemを集めます。</font></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
