  <tr> 
    <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><font size="2"><b>Heart of Ice、Sabertooth Tiger Mane、Shaman 
      Powder、Ton Warrior TotemをLuminare Pasiniaに渡します。</b></font> <font size="2"><br>
      <br>
      Luminare Pasinia places the items into a sack and removes a scroll from 
      her robe. This is yours. A spell I discovered and translated for one with 
      less intelligence than the great Luminare of Firiona Vie. You may kiss my 
      feet now.<br>
